com.atc.simulator.prediction_service.engine.workers

Class PredictionWorkerThread

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atc.simulator.prediction_service.engine.workers.PredictionWorkerThread
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RunnableThread, java.lang.Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JavaPredictionWorkerThread, OpenCLPredictionWorkerThread

    public abstract class PredictionWorkerThread
extends java.lang.Object
implements RunnableThread
    A worker who can work on PredictionWorkItem s that the PredictionEngineThread gives to it. Has at least one internal thread. Could be subclassed to create opencl workers.
